Institutions authenticating personal identity
(1) Mining wallets launch certifications through the DApp , and submit application information to the IDBook chain.
(2) The certificate authentication of citizens is carried out by the issuing nodes(super nodes), and other identity authentications are carried out by the institutional nodes.
(3) Institutions perform certification duties to authenticate the identity information.
(4) The institutions complete an identity confirmation by signing the mining wallet address and writing the transaction into the blockchain.

